<paragraph id="FA6F538434A596020B7A63A4EF1E234B" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EFBA08133C2819C9B810E961A0635C2F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
MEXICO. Oaxaca, Pochutla, Mun. Santa Maria Huatulco, 
<emphasis id="2AD556728F3AACCF9A9C2915E5E271C1" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">E. Carranza et al.</emphasis>
